translations.OpenStreetMap integration provides a sea:
OpenStreetMap integration provides a search provider for locations, a reference
provider to render location links from various map services (OpenStreetMap, Google maps...) and a custom link picker
component to quickly insert a location link by searching or selecting a point on an (awesome) interactive map.
translations.Warning, everything you type in the Unif: Warning, everything you type in the Unified Search menu will be sent to OpenStreetMap's Nominatim service.
